Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:59.01,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}虽然想去好好梳理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.06,0:01:06.66,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}但唯独真正想传达的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:12.60,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}纠葛不清说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:18.25,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}轻轻地深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:27.11,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}愿这温柔的希望能持续到永久
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:30.61,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}能否看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.91,0:01:33.74,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.05,0:01:39.84,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}指尖描绘出的路标
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:42.92,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}能否传递到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.92,0:01:46.82,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}我愿今天也能继续欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.82,0:01:51.80,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}你明天也能充满笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.17,0:02:01.02,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}一定 一定
